## Only extract complex logic into helper functions

Example of inlining a simple helper for `onVersionChange` :w


```typescript
    <VersionSelector
        selectedVersionId={selectedVersionId}
        filterVersions={sortedFilterVersions}
        onVersionChange={(versionId) => setSelectedVersionId(versionId)}
        onCreateVersion={handleCreateVersion}
    />

```